= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) World Map =

This page documents the world map and locations in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

The world of Dragon Warrior IV spans multiple continents across five chapters. Each chapter focuses on different regions and characters before all converge in Chapter 5.

